### ========================================
### Autofix Test Flow - 3 Sites
### Endpoint: PATCH /sites/:siteId/opportunities/:opportunityId/suggestions/auto-fix
### Required: suggestion in NEW or PENDING_VALIDATION + site has auto_fix access
###          + configuration has `${oppType}-auto-fix` handler enabled for site
###
### Workflow per site:
###   1. GET site                         -> sanity check
###   2. GET opportunities                -> pick an oppId with an autofix-able type
###   3. GET suggestions for opp          -> grab suggestionIds + see current status
###   4. PATCH suggestions status -> NEW  -> reset state if not already NEW
###   5. PATCH .../auto-fix               -> trigger autofix
### ========================================

@DEV_HOST=spacecat.experiencecloud.live
@apiKey=aab2c470-7708-013c-664a-7ea0e1f7f5af

# IMS user token (Bearer) - REQUIRED for the auto-fix PATCH unless you have a
# `promiseToken` cookie. Without it, suggestions.js calls getIMSPromiseToken()
# which needs Authorization: Bearer <IMS token> and returns 400 otherwise.
# Grab a fresh one from the UI / IMS - tokens expire.
@imsToken=eyJhbGciOiJSUzI1NiIsIng1dSI6Imltc19uYTEtc3RnMS1rZXktYXQtMS5jZXIiLCJraWQiOiJpbXNfbmExLXN0ZzEta2V5LWF0LTEiLCJpdHQiOiJhdCJ9..OchN2DGVMuOwQTMPgvZP5jE8DWJe2lchx_w26Vyp9Yzukbk82fHgMXqiqSa9X1Vc9TgUs33XP_AyFc_-DxgxnJBkkJaXtq2SbMjR7hH75j_D15AU-12pK7Mff756c_nwq_8XuZCuWrxm90G4reKt8axPh6Efhjpe_TELNDDTVXT5gwMqcajHYLDu4wQH-GHrZp_HNl4Ja9MThqgkWQKlD4P44gf4T4aEAje0qRY2F3NwuZTZjpZyP0qFnlU9RewU1JAi6CyUOVMQyqrtJi4SgKq-SEM2fNyhfiXLgTwOegNY5jtS9xo7t2JDCAcI-gKCCTgtoskOiPj9QdzSquwGKg

# --- Sites under test (org 44568c3e-efd4-4a7f-8ecd-8caf615f836c)
# site1: GOOGLE DRIVE  (content.source.type=drive.google) - main--wknd-backlink-test--mimchome.aem.live
# site2: SHAREPOINT EXTERNAL (onedrive @ adobeenterprisesupportaem.sharepoint.com) - main--wknd-backlink-test-sharepoint-external--mimchome.aem.live
# site3: SHAREPOINT (onedrive @ adobe.sharepoint.com) - main--wknd-backlink-test-sharepoint--mimchome.aem.live
@site1=5810d40e-b39b-4da8-8a9b-03a67c1f8aaf
@site2=9763ba2c-d78c-415d-8561-3e33ee6c1954
@site3=eeda97b6-87fd-47a6-b66d-cd0f99a9b3d4

# --- Per-site broken-backlinks oppId + suggestionId
# All three sites have a `broken-backlinks` opp (matches their mysticatLegacyAutofixBridgeOpportunities).
# Other opps available on each site (NEW): security-csp on all three; cwv + alt-text on site1.

# site1: 2 suggestions, BOTH currently FIXED -> step 4 (reset to NEW) is REQUIRED
@opp1=7939bb77-a5a1-48f0-b37e-e611c995e564
@suggestion1=aa85c227-037f-457c-9113-387e4748126b
# alt: c340f060-ab5a-4433-aff5-9e693f37a859 (also FIXED, /magazines)

# site2: 5 suggestions, 4 already NEW -> reset is optional
@opp2=05c1ce88-332a-4fb5-b7ea-9c7ff884afd3
@suggestion2=3258f307-2789-4746-ac2f-90439b2a5663
# other NEW: b08cd829-b7b9-4446-9765-62c66ae91ac6, 51812b55-8895-417f-a601-5a7ed56ea86b, bf72b3e2-678d-484f-92fd-de0d7aed5b84

# site3: 4 suggestions, 3 already NEW -> reset is optional
@opp3=6287ec34-a954-4eda-b2aa-bf4999f175ed
@suggestion3=86fbd3a2-afc2-4d39-bf10-b5cfc021a8f1
# other NEW: c9bddc9c-3757-489d-a8e8-a6a6e4c74f4f, a80944f5-940b-414c-aad2-4d26af2ddfb0

### ========================================
### Configuration sanity check
### Verify ${oppType}-auto-fix handler is enabled for the sites
### Look for entries like "broken-backlinks-auto-fix", "alt-text-auto-fix", etc.
### ========================================

### Get latest configuration
GET https://{{DEV_HOST}}/api/ci/configurations/latest
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

### ========================================
### SITE 1: GOOGLE DRIVE
### 5810d40e-b39b-4da8-8a9b-03a67c1f8aaf
### main--wknd-backlink-test--mimchome.aem.live
### deliveryConfig.mysticatLegacyAutofixBridgeOpportunities = ["broken_backlinks"]  (underscore)
### ========================================

### 1. Get site
GET https://{{DEV_HOST}}/api/ci/sites/{{site1}}
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

### 2. List opportunities (pick autofix-able type, copy id into @opp1)
GET https://{{DEV_HOST}}/api/ci/sites/{{site1}}/opportunities
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

### 2b. (alternative) Only NEW opportunities
GET https://{{DEV_HOST}}/api/ci/sites/{{site1}}/opportunities/by-status/NEW
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

### 3. List suggestions for chosen opportunity (copy a suggestion id into @suggestion1)
GET https://{{DEV_HOST}}/api/ci/sites/{{site1}}/opportunities/{{opp1}}/suggestions
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

### 4. Reset suggestion status to NEW (so autofix accepts it)
PATCH https://{{DEV_HOST}}/api/ci/sites/{{site1}}/opportunities/{{opp1}}/suggestions/status
Content-Type: application/json
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

[
  { "id": "{{suggestion1}}", "status": "NEW" }
]

### 5. Trigger autofix (needs Bearer for IMS promise token)
PATCH https://{{DEV_HOST}}/api/ci/sites/{{site1}}/opportunities/{{opp1}}/suggestions/auto-fix
Content-Type: application/json
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}
Authorization: Bearer {{imsToken}}

{
  "suggestionIds": ["{{suggestion1}}"]
}

### ========================================
### SITE 2: SHAREPOINT EXTERNAL
### 9763ba2c-d78c-415d-8561-3e33ee6c1954
### main--wknd-backlink-test-sharepoint-external--mimchome.aem.live
### onedrive @ adobeenterprisesupportaem.sharepoint.com (non-Adobe-corp tenant)
### authoringType = documentauthoring;  no mysticatLegacyAutofixBridgeOpportunities
### ========================================

### 1. Get site
GET https://{{DEV_HOST}}/api/ci/sites/{{site2}}
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

### 2. List opportunities
GET https://{{DEV_HOST}}/api/ci/sites/{{site2}}/opportunities
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

### 2b. NEW only
GET https://{{DEV_HOST}}/api/ci/sites/{{site2}}/opportunities/by-status/NEW
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

### 3. List suggestions
GET https://{{DEV_HOST}}/api/ci/sites/{{site2}}/opportunities/{{opp2}}/suggestions
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

### 4. Reset suggestion status to NEW
PATCH https://{{DEV_HOST}}/api/ci/sites/{{site2}}/opportunities/{{opp2}}/suggestions/status
Content-Type: application/json
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

[
  { "id": "{{suggestion2}}", "status": "NEW" }
]

### 5. Trigger autofix (needs Bearer for IMS promise token)
PATCH https://{{DEV_HOST}}/api/ci/sites/{{site2}}/opportunities/{{opp2}}/suggestions/auto-fix
Content-Type: application/json
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}
Authorization: Bearer {{imsToken}}

{
  "suggestionIds": ["{{suggestion2}}"]
}

### ========================================
